    List all available platforms from refine.bio

    rb_platforms.Rd

    List all available platforms from refine.bio

    rb_platforms(client = RefineBio::RefineBio())

    Value

    a 2-column `data.frame`

    Examples

    
plats = rb_platforms()
head(plats)
#>    platform_accession_code
#> 1             IonTorrentS5
#> 2              ovigene10st
#> 3                  GPL4861
#> 4 Illumina_MouseRef-8_v2.0
#> 5                 GPL16365
#> 6                 GPL16275
#>                                                         platform_name
#> 1                                                      Ion Torrent S5
#> 2                            [OviGene-1_0-st] Ovine Gene 1.1 ST Array
#> 3                         Swegene Human 27K RAP (positions from file)
#> 4          Illumina MouseRef-8 v2.0 expression beadchip (ILMN_SYMBOL)
#> 5                                  Candida albicans tiling ChIP array
#> 6 Agilent-035430 mouse miRNA array (miRNA_107_Sep09 miRNA ID version)
